Matla a golomente ya profense a fokoditswe go lebana le dilo tse di leng ka mo [[:en:Constitution_of_South_Africa|constritution ya naga]]. Tse dingwe tsa dilo tse ke :  temothuo, thuto, boitekanelo le tsa matlo a sechaba<span> </span>&#x2013;&#x20;matla a profense a arogantswe le a golomente ya bosetshaba, e e nang le tumello ya go dira melao le melawana e golomente ya profense e ka e latelang; mme mo tse dingwe golomente ya profense e na matla otlhe.<ref>'[[wikisource:Constitution of the Republic of South Africa, 1996|Constitution of the Republic of South Africa, 1996]]'', [[wikisource:Constitution of the Republic of South Africa, 1996/Chapter 6|"Chapter 6: Provinces"]]. ''</ref>

